{"id": "1420092262087393402", "channel_id": "1420091516944126085", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@&1419930759182942309>", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T16:59:39.320000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1420091516944126085", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "The meaning of 对抗塞卡    戒备提升", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1410391772894330961", "1412867203514236942"]}
{"id": "1420118410188161116", "channel_id": "1420091516944126085", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Probably it refers to to the enemy intention of “adding symptoms/status cards into your deck”\nAs Alva’s burst discard all those cards\n塞means “adding (negative cards)” here", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T18:43:33.513000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍🏻", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1420091516944126085", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "The meaning of 对抗塞卡    戒备提升", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1410391772894330961", "1412867203514236942"]}
