{"id": "1419865464628314164", "channel_id": "1419179851272814602", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "This <#1408302426833817662> seems really relevant to this discussion... We have a lot of eager people in this project, translating gameplay things from EN -> their language...\n\nShould I treat this as a crisis and double-time my proofreading of Gameplay wording? 😅 or am I just being OCD again", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T01:58:26.592000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-23T02:05:44.673000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1419179851272814602", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "如何解決翻譯與校對人員的同步編輯衝突問題？", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1410391772894330961", "1404748570871201913"]}
{"id": "1419866232529621045", "channel_id": "1419179851272814602", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "it feels really bad to me to have people do WEEKS (or cumulatively, MONTHS) of work translating from EN -> their language just to realize that the gameplay text in EN was bad or in some cases literally wrong, and restart their work with the new EN text when I or BIAV gets around to it", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T02:01:29.674000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1419179851272814602", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "如何解決翻譯與校對人員的同步編輯衝突問題？", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1410391772894330961", "1404748570871201913"]}
{"id": "1419867140718067792", "channel_id": "1419179851272814602", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "like... I could probably bang out all of the WoDs in a day or two, and resubmit that for folks to work on through my system.\nbut FUCK then I'm in the \"sweeping changes\" dilemma I was getting wall-of-awful'd by again <:loadingcat:950667225008840755> \nI feel like I should just do what needs to be done so that no one is working with bad gameplay text anymore. If BIAV wants to override all of my EN work later down the line that's fine, but anyone put in honest effort translating gameplay into their language should be working from a consistent base that cleanly communicates mechanics instead of the MTL mess.", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T02:05:06.203000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1419179851272814602", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "如何解決翻譯與校對人員的同步編輯衝突問題？", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1410391772894330961", "1404748570871201913"]}
